  "Quadratics":"Quadratic formula: x=(âˆ’bآ±âˆڑ(bآ²âˆ’4ac))/(2a). Factoring may be faster when the numbers are friendly.",
  "Complex Numbers":"Powers of i repeat every four: i, âˆ’1, âˆ’i, 1.",
